<h1>Directory of Clothing and Accessories Resources</h1>

    <p>
        <a href="/">Home</a> >
            <a href="/Home">Home</a>  >             <a href="/Home/Consumer_Information">Consumer Information</a>  >             <a href="/Home/Consumer_Information/Clothing_and_Accessories">Clothing and Accessories</a>         </p>

<p><p>Clothing and Accessories is a consumer information and education category featuring sites on clothing, fashion, style, clothing care, wardrobe tips and strategies, and related topics. It is designed to help consumers find news and information about clothing and style. While it covers articles on shopping and shopping strategies, it is NOT designed for shopping sites, which should be listed in the appropriate shopping category.</p></p>

<h2>Subcategories</h2>
<ul id="triple">
    <li><a href="/Home/Consumer_Information/Clothing_and_Accessories/Clothing_Care" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Clothing Care</strong></a></li>
