<h2>Resources in This Category</h2>
<ul>

    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.arashmazinani.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Arash Mazinani</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.arashmazinani.com/</strong></font> <br /> A site dedicated to style advice, fashion tips and trend updates for men and women.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.buyingclothingonline.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Buying Clothing Online</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.buyingclothingonline.com/</strong></font> <br /> Background information on online ordering, security, return policies, size charts and shipping.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="https://chicisimo.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Chicisimo</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>https://chicisimo.com/</strong></font> <br /> User-driven site showcasing personal fashion and style, with a best-of section selected each week and month.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.cluelessfashionista.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Clueless Fashionista</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.cluelessfashionista.com/</strong></font> <br /> Offers easy to understand fashion tips for those people that want to be more fashionable but aren&#039;t sure how.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.collegegrad.com/jobsearch/15-5.shtml" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>CollegeGrad.com: Dress for Interview Success</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.collegegrad.com/jobsearch/15-5.shtml</strong></font> <br /> How to dress well for a job interview.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.fashion-411.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Fashion 411</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.fashion-411.com/</strong></font> <br /> Fashion trends, wardrobe advice for petite, tall and plus-size women, and other useful articles. Fee required for some sections.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.fashionafter50.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Fashion After 50</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.fashionafter50.com/</strong></font> <br /> Free fashion archetype quiz helps older women rediscover their inner goddess and style preferences. Advice about how to dress, news about trends.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://fashionicon.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Fashion Icon</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://fashionicon.com/</strong></font> <br /> Features dressing tips and articles, an &quot;ask the fashion experts&quot; column, and fun craft projects for recycling dated fads.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.fashiontrial.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Fashion Trial</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.fashiontrial.com/</strong></font> <br /> Ask a fashion related question and upload your photos. Others can then vote between your looks or outfits.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.fitnesstravelgear.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Fitness Travel Gear</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.fitnesstravelgear.com/</strong></font> <br /> Features reviews of hiking boots, running apparel, packs and luggage, and digital devices. Includes some shopping links.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.gotryiton.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Go Try It On</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.gotryiton.com/</strong></font> <br /> Offers an opportunity to get a second opinion on an outfit using a webcam or uploaded photo, as well as shopping advice and the ability to rate others&#039; outfits.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.howstuffworks.com/computer-clothing.htm" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>How Stuff Works: How Computerized Clothing Will Work</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.howstuffworks.com/computer-clothing.htm</strong></font> <br /> Illustrated narrative shows how computerized clothes will be the next step in making computers and devices portable.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.85b.org/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>International Bra and Dress Size Calculators and Converters</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.85b.org/</strong></font> <br /> Includes bra size calculator, bra size converter and dress size converter.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://jacquistafford.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Jacqui Stafford's Fabulous, Fashionable Life</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://jacquistafford.com/</strong></font> <br /> Shape fashion and beauty editor Jacqui Stafford provides expert advice through video segments.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.jeansinfo.org/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Jeans Manufacturers</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.jeansinfo.org/</strong></font> <br /> How jeans&#039; manufacturers make blue jeans and what to know when buying or ordering them.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.leahfeldon.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Leah Feldon</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.leahfeldon.com/</strong></font> <br /> Advice from style guru with fashion tips, style advice and finding good buys.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.leatherhandbags.org/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Leather Handbags</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.leatherhandbags.org/</strong></font> <br /> Guide explaining the different types and brands of handbags.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.look-fabulous.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Look Fabulous</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.look-fabulous.com/</strong></font> <br /> Advice website aimed at helping women get the right look with their clothing and body shapes, and their hairstyles and face shapes.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.lovely-living.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Lovely Living</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.lovely-living.com/</strong></font> <br /> A weblog on fashion, shopping, style, cooking, cosmetics, writing and the arts.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://mod.today/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Mod.today</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://mod.today/</strong></font> <br /> Articles on fashion, hair and lifestyle.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://moderntraditional.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Modern Traditional Clothing</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://moderntraditional.com/</strong></font> <br /> Forums, search, auctions and information about various ethnic, tribal and traditional styles and current fashions. Updates weekly by way of subscription newsletter.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.mouthshut.com/read.php?cid=14" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>MouthShut.com</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.mouthshut.com/read.php?cid=14</strong></font> <br /> Gives consumers a chance to review their favourite and most hated brands of clothing, shoes and accessories, and groups them under user-friendly categories.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://necktieaficionado.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Necktie Aficionado</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://necktieaficionado.com/</strong></font> <br /> Necktie resource on buying, how to tie a tie, the latest looks, and care.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://outfitideashq.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Outfit Ideas HQ</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://outfitideashq.com/</strong></font> <br /> A fashion blog with fashion advice and style tips.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
