	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.quicksize.fr/</strong></font> <br /> Conversion tables for clothing, divided into categories (shoes, skirts, jeans, shirts, etc.), for men, women and children.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.savvies.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Savvies</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.savvies.com/</strong></font> <br /> Guide to shopping and style, with weekly newsletter and video podcast.</p>
