	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.shefinds.com/</strong></font> <br /> New York-based site with trend reports and personal shopping events. Newsletter available.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.styleclarity.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Style Clarity</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.styleclarity.com/</strong></font> <br /> Articles and resources pages covering wardrobe planning, fashion and style.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.stylepilot.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Style Pilot</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.stylepilot.com/</strong></font> <br /> An online personal stylist for men.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.style-yourself-confident.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Style Yourself Confident</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.style-yourself-confident.com/</strong></font> <br /> A free information website on how to do your own style makeover with a series of simple questions.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.swapstyle.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Swapstyle.com</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.swapstyle.com/</strong></font> <br /> Swap fashionable clothing and cosmetics with women from all around the world. Includes forum and magazine.</p>
    </li>	
